  "title": "ELECTRICIAN",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Install, maintain, and repair electrical systems, wiring, and fixtures in accordance with local and national electrical codes.</p></li><li><p>Diagnose and troubleshoot electrical faults to carry out timely and effective repairs.</p></li><li><p>Inspect electrical systems, components, and equipment to identify defects, damage, or operational issues.</p></li><li><p>Read and interpret technical drawings, blueprints, and schematics to ensure accurate wiring and system specifications.</p></li><li><p>Work closely with team members, contractors, and clients to plan and complete electrical work efficiently.</p></li><li><p>Follow all safety regulations, company procedures, and industry standards to minimize risks and ensure a safe working environment.</p></li></ul>",
